c: 11
v: 3
t: "Uye kuti: “Kumbirai ruregerero rwaTenzi venyu, uye motendeukira kwavari muchikumbira ruregerero, kuti vave vanokupai mufaro wakanaka wenguva yakatarwa, uye kupa muridzi wemakomborero (uyo anobatsira vanotambura pachake, uye nehupfume wake kana mashoko akanaka) makomborero ake. Asi mukava munofuratira, nokudaro zvirokwazvo ndinokutyirai marwadzo ezuva hombe (Zuva Rokutongwa).”"